verses.text:
Work-ing, O Christ, with thee, Work-ing with thee;
I know that thy glo-ry will shine on me, Work-ing with thee;
Sav-ior, my heart with thee, Work-ing with thee,
As work of thine calls for me, Can nev-er be Na-tion or Na-tion.

Work-ing, O Christ, with thee, Work-ing with thee;
I know that thy might wil at-tend on me, Work-ing with thee;
Sav-ior, my heart with thee, Work-ing with thee,
As work of thine calls for me, Can nev-er be Na-tion or Na-tion.

Work-ing, O Christ, with thee, Work-ing with thee;
I know that thy love will de-scend on me, Work-ing with thee;
Sav-ior, my heart with thee, Work-ing with thee,
As work of thine calls for me, Can nev-er be Na-tion or Na-tion.
